nse to FLASH irradiation. We found that an increment in the k value is\ngenerally more protective of tumor than normal tissue due to a higher frequency\nof lower pO2 values in tumors. Variation in the g value affects the dose at\nwhich oxygen depletion impacts response, but does not alter the dose dependent\nresponse trends, if the g value is identical in both tumor and normal tissue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Jan 2022 23:49:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jul 2022 04:40:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 17 Dec 2022 08:26:02 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 01:55:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-29"}
