and valence quark effects. These\nfindings could be useful to guide low-energy models and effective theories of\nQCD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2022 07:11:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Jan 2022 01:45:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Feb 2022 03:01:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
