l region under splicing attack. Results show that our proposed method,\ntailored to the nature of SAR signals, provides better performances than\nstate-of-the-art forensic tools developed for natural images.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2022 11:42:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 19:22:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 3 Apr 2022 08:27:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-05"}
